message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm actually really happy with my current policy, but I have a question about my coverage.
That's great to hear that you're happy with your policy! Before we dive in, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Of course, my full name is Sarah Johnson.
Thank you for completing security, Sarah. How can I assist you with your coverage question today?
I was wondering if my policy covers rental car insurance when I travel overseas?
Great question, Sarah! Let me check that for you. One moment, please.
Take your time, Chris. I appreciate your help!
I'm glad we could help, Sarah. It looks like your current policy does not include rental car insurance overseas. Would you like to add that coverage?
Oh, I was really hoping it would be included. Is there a way to add it now or any other options available?
Certainly, Sarah. A possible resolution could be to add an international rental car insurance rider to your existing policy. Would that work for you?
That sounds like a good option. How much would that cost me?
Let me check the pricing for you, Sarah. One moment, please.
Thank you, Chris. I appreciate your help with this.
After reviewing the options, adding the international rental car insurance rider would cost an additional $20 per month. Does this work for you?
That's a bit more than I expected. I think I'll pass for now. Thank you for looking into it, though, Chris.
I completely understand, Sarah. If you ever change your mind or have any other questions in the future, feel free to reach out. We're here to help.
Thank you, Chris. I appreciate your assistance today.
You are welcome, Sarah. Have a great day!
